內向本院提出抗告狀。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　10　　月　　7 　　日\r\n                              書記官    莊琬婷","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/111%2c%e5%96%ae%e7%a6%81%e6%b2%92%2c218%2c20221007%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,111,單禁沒,218,20221007,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"單禁沒","JNO":"218","JDATE":"20221007","JTITLE":"聲請單獨宣告沒收違禁物"}